<div id="pf4608" class="pf w53 h2f5" data-page-no="4608"><div class="pc pc4608 w53 h2f5"><div class="t m1083 xc6 h5 y2f78 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 2 July 6-12 </div><div class="t m2461 x10 h10c y2b53 ff4 fs43 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">e2TB [I:Ammo</div><div class="t m46e1 xad h10c y2b53 ff4 fs43 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m21f5 xa3 h10c y2b53 ff4 fs43 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12r </div><div class="t m3b0 x93 h10c y2a48 ff4 fs43 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">arg.11Ek </div><div class="t m834 xd3 h5 y228a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I was born with nothing, and I will </div><div class="t me60 xd6 h5 y2349 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lie with nothing. The Lord gave, and </div><div class="t mcdb xd6 h5 y148f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">low he has taken away. May his name </div><div class="t mf5 xd6 h5 y51d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">)e praised!&quot; (Job 1:21, TEV). </div><div class="t m179 xd3 h5 y774 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;When God sends us something </div><div class="t m5a3 x93 h5 y15a6 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">;ood, we welcome it. How can we </div><div class="t m403 xd6 h5 ycfc ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">complain when he sends us trouble?&quot; </div><div class="t m2a0 xd6 h5 y1bbd ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job 2:10, TEV). </div><div class="t m54b xc3 h35 yef3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">On the twenty-fourth day of </div><div class="t m109 x93 h35 y7a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">December 1974 life was as usual in the </div><div class="t m1ac xd6 h35 y81d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Australian city of Darwin. People were </div><div class="t m745 x93 h35 y2d9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">doing their Christmas shopping, </div><div class="t m8d3 x93 h35 y9d6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">wrapping gifts, preparing for loved </div><div class="t m112 x93 h35 y7cf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ones, decorating their homes. </div><div class="t m2b2 x93 h35 yc6c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Warnings came of an impending </div><div class="t m2ea x93 h35 y1d1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cyclone, but the citizens of the city had </div><div class="t ma35 x93 h35 yced ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">seen high winds before and were not </div><div class="t mb8e x93 h35 y3bc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">greatly alarmed. Then the winds </div><div class="t m9b1 x93 h35 y1255 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">struck-160 milesper hour in velocity. </div><div class="t m2aa x93 h35 y3f2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ninety percent of the city was </div><div class="t m586 x93 h35 y4ad ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">destroyed. Thousands were </div><div class="t m5cc x93 h35 y59b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">homeless. A reported 45 persons lost </div><div class="t m747 x93 h35 y8ba ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their lives, and many more were </div><div class="t m860 x93 h35 y3d6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">injured. One television report showed </div><div class="t m5ce x93 h35 y12bd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a man in a hospital bed. He and his </div><div class="t m1c7 x93 h35 y906 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">family had crouched in their yard </div><div class="t m2ee x93 h35 y12e5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">while their house was completely </div><div class="t m699 x93 h35 y473 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">destroyed. The wife and mother was </div><div class="t m188 xd6 h35 ye5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">killed. For this family, disaster struck </div><div class="t m480 xd6 h35 ye88 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tragically all in a day. </div><div class="t m6a7 xb4 h35 y75e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Since then more and perhaps </div><div class="t mf3f xd6 h35 y1257 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">greater calamities have taken place in </div><div class="t m8ca xd6 h35 yc3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this world. For millions of people </div><div class="t m173d xd6 h35 ycc4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disaster will strike—sometimes from  </div><div class="t m3a0 xaf h35 y28bb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">natural causes, others because of </div><div class="t me4 xaf h35 y2349 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sickness and accident, and perhaps </div><div class="t mad7 xaf h35 y1491 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">others—God forbid—because of war. </div><div class="t m747 xaf h35 y1155 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">No doubt some who study these </div><div class="t m3b3 xaf h35 y760 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lessons will know how Job felt when </div><div class="t m44e xaf h35 y15a6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disaster struck for him. May God grant </div><div class="t m78a xaf h35 ycfc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that Job&apos;s experience may help to </div><div class="t m1391 xaf h35 y1bbd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rebuild broken lives. </div><div class="t md3 x20 h35 yfad ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Job does not set out to answer the </div><div class="t m4ad xaf h35 yef3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">problem of suffering, but instead </div><div class="t m433 xaf h35 y7a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shows that even a righteous man can </div><div class="t mbc1 xaf h35 y81d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">utilize such an experience as that </div><div class="t m7cc xaf h35 y9b1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through which the hero passed to </div><div class="t m21c xaf h35 y9d7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">attain to new heights of emotional and </div><div class="t m8f9 xaf h35 y7cf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritual maturity. Quite obviously </div><div class="t m48b xaf h35 yc6c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nobody can be exempt from suffering, </div><div class="t m6df xaf h35 y1d1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for where there are men there will </div><div class="t m860 xaf h35 yced ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">always be emotional and mental </div><div class="t m862 xaf h35 y3bc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">conflicts, with corresponding adverse </div><div class="t m87b xaf h35 y7af ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">effects. The supreme exemplar of the </div><div class="t m87b xaf h35 y3f2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">righteous sufferer was Jesus Christ, </div><div class="t m188 xaf h35 y4ac ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">who neither explained nor dismissed </div><div class="t mf55 x2b h35 y7f7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">suffering, but instead absorbed it into </div><div class="t mb47 xaf h35 y1012 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His own spiritual experience, and </div><div class="t me12 xaf h35 y217 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through His fellowship with God </div><div class="t m2d4 xaf h35 ycef ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">achieved what Rowley has happily </div><div class="t m1470 x2b h35 y96e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">styled &apos;the wresting of profit from the </div><div class="t mf22 x2b h35 y4e9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">suffering,&apos; which has been of </div><div class="t m342 x2b h35 y7b6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">incalculable value to subsequent </div><div class="t m3b1 x2b h35 ya4e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">humanity.&quot;—R. K. Harrison, </div><div class="t m858 xaf h35 y20 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Introduction to the Old Testament </div><div class="t m9e8 x2b h35 ya4f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Grand Rapids, Mich.: Wm. B. </div><div class="t m851 x2b h35 yb1c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Eerdmans Publishing Co., 1969), p. </div><div class="t m560 xaf h35 y54a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1046. </div><div class="t m9b4 x2b h5 y252 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m23f x2b h5 ya52 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t mc4 x5a h5 yb1d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Before the Storm </div><div class="t ma3b x5a h5 y47c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 1:2, 3) </div><div class="t m558 x2b h5 y79c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m268 x5a h5 y9a5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Trouble Brewing </div><div class="t mcfa x5a h5 y186 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 1:9-11) </div><div class="t mb7 x2b h5 y4f2 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t maa3 x5a h5 y6d8 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Tragedy Strikes </div><div class="t mb4b x5a h5 y36f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 1:18, 19) </div><div class="t m1ce x2b h5 y57a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m356 x5a h5 y57b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Initial Responses </div><div class="t m380 x5a h5 y3c5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 1:20-22) </div><div class="t m8a8 x2b h5 yd4a ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m14a x5a h5 y7c3 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Three &quot;Friends&quot; </div><div class="t m146f xb0 h5 ya7f ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 2:11, 12) </div><div class="t m2ef x1f h5 y4a0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t mc4 xb0 h5 ye8d ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Light Grows Dim </div><div class="t m871 xb0 h5 ye8e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 3:2-7) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
